  "model_paragraph": "The two maps show a town before and after reconstruction. Overall, this industrial area has undergone gentrification, and the town centre has been pedestrianised. Prior to the changes, there was a harbour in the south and two factories facing the water. A road headed north until it reached a crossing, where it forked into two: the right fork led to a residential area of one-storey houses, while the left went towards a rural area. Following the reconstruction, the factories were replaced by a museum, shops and a restaurant, and a tunnel was added under the city.",
